# Trivy ignorelist — CVE IDs we have evaluated and explicitly accept.
#
# Format:   <CVE-ID>            # YYYY-MM-DD: <pkg> — short justification
# Or:       <CVE-ID> exp:<YYYY-MM-DD>  # auto-expires after that date
#
# Each entry MUST include a justification comment. If a CVE later affects
# a code path we actually exercise, remove it from this file and address
# the underlying dependency.
#
# When you bump a dependency that fixed a CVE upstream, prune the entry
# so the ignorelist stays an accurate audit trail rather than tech debt.
#
# Currently empty — add CVEs here when a transitive dep we don't exercise
# at runtime keeps tripping the scanner and a real fix isn't feasible
# (e.g. base-image CVEs without upstream patches; npm-bundled deps in
# tooling we don't ship).
